name: Ludmilla El Golilla - retro Oakley Eyeshade Vers.
description:
Ludmilla is a primate that loves to change look and to get crazy when the music hits! This is the 2# NFT of a ongoing collection, with it we want to raise awareness for the beauty of different characters and styles we have on this loco planet!

This version inspired by the legendary eyeshade-sunglasses released in the 80s by Oakley. They started as cycling-specific glasses but turned into loved generic sport glasses as soon they hitted the market

3D Sculpting | Rendering | Hair Simulation | mp4 loop 1280x1280px | SELFMADE MUSIC
